abstract: The Democrats have a historically diverse field, but the Asian-American entrepreneur will be debating with six white candidates.
snippet: The Democrats have a historically diverse field, but the Asian-American entrepreneur will be debating with six white candidates.
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — It is a fact of political life Representative Judy Chu is accustomed to: when there is a discussion about people of color in Washington, she will inevitably have to elbow her way in so that Asian-Americans are considered.

abstract: Just seven Democrats will take the stage for the sixth and final round of presidential debates in 2019. That's down from 20 candidates six months ago.
snippet: Just seven Democrats will take the stage for the sixth and final round of presidential debates in 2019. That's down from 20 candidates six months ago.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Just seven Democrats will take the stage for the sixth and final round of presidential debates in 2019. That's down from 20 candidates six months ago.
headline_main: 6 Big Questions Ahead of Democrats' Final Debate of 2019
headline_print_headline: 6 Big Questions Ahead of Democrats' Final Debate of 2019

abstract: The long-festering feud between Elizabeth Warren and Pete Buttigieg erupted Thursday night in a high-stakes debate that tested the strength of the Democratic Party's shrinking pool of presidential contenders just six weeks before primary voting begins.
snippet: The long-festering feud between Elizabeth Warren and Pete Buttigieg erupted Thursday night in a high-stakes debate that tested the strength of the Democratic Party's shrinking pool of presidential contenders just six weeks before primary voting be...
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — The long-festering feud between Elizabeth Warren and Pete Buttigieg erupted Thursday night in a high-stakes debate that tested the strength of the Democratic Party's shrinking pool of presidential contenders just six weeks before primary voting begins.
headline_main: Buttigieg-Warren Clash on Campaign Trail Spills Into Debate
headline_print_headline: Buttigieg-Warren Clash on Campaign Trail Spills Into Debate

abstract: Donald Trump became the third U.S. president to be impeached as the House of Representatives formally charged him on Wednesday with abuse of power and obstructing Congress.
snippet: Donald Trump became the third U.S. president to be impeached as the House of Representatives formally charged him on Wednesday with abuse of power and obstructing Congress.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - Donald Trump became the third U.S. president to be impeached as the House of Representatives formally charged him on Wednesday with abuse of power and obstructing Congress.
headline_main: Instant View: Donald Trump Becomes Third U.S. President to Be Impeached

headline_main: Here’s What We’re Watching After Impeachment

abstract: The president traveled to Michigan, a vital electoral state, to deliver his response after he became the third president to be impeached by the House.
snippet: The president traveled to Michigan, a vital electoral state, to deliver his response after he became the third president to be impeached by the House.
lead_paragraph: BATTLE CREEK, Mich. — President Trump angrily responded to the impeachment he had long been dreading on Wednesday, lashing out at his Democratic accusers in a rambling two-hour speech and calling for their defeat in November.

abstract: Elizabeth Warren has recalibrated her rhetoric on Medicare for All, as concerns about her support for replacing private insurance with a government-run plan continue to buffet her once-surging Democratic presidential campaign.
snippet: Elizabeth Warren has recalibrated her rhetoric on Medicare for All, as concerns about her support for replacing private insurance with a government-run plan continue to buffet her once-surging Democratic presidential campaign.
lead_paragraph: CLINTON, Iowa — Elizabeth Warren has recalibrated her rhetoric on Medicare for All, as concerns about her support for replacing private insurance with a government-run plan continue to buffet her once-surging Democratic presidential campaign.
headline_main: Seeking Fresh Momentum, Democrat Warren Recalibrates 'Medicare for All' Rhetoric
headline_print_headline: Seeking Fresh Momentum, Democrat Warren Recalibrates 'Medicare for All' Rhetoric

abstract: On a day when the U.S. House of Representatives debated whether President Donald Trump should be removed from office, members of his administration fanned out across the country to make the case that the president is steadily getting the job done.
snippet: On a day when the U.S. House of Representatives debated whether President Donald Trump should be removed from office, members of his administration fanned out across the country to make the case that the president is steadily getting the job done....
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — On a day when the U.S. House of Representatives debated whether President Donald Trump should be removed from office, members of his administration fanned out across the country to make the case that the president is steadily getting the job done.
headline_main: As Impeachment Looms, Trump Officials Look to Change the Subject
headline_print_headline: As Impeachment Looms, Trump Officials Look to Change the Subject

abstract: A winnowed field of Democratic presidential contenders takes the debate stage Thursday for a sixth and final time in 2019, as candidates seek to convince anxious voters that they are the party's best hope to deny President Donald Trump a second term.
snippet: A winnowed field of Democratic presidential contenders takes the debate stage Thursday for a sixth and final time in 2019, as candidates seek to convince anxious voters that they are the party's best hope to deny President Donald Trump a second te...
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — A winnowed field of Democratic presidential contenders takes the debate stage Thursday for a sixth and final time in 2019, as candidates seek to convince anxious voters that they are the party's best hope to deny President Donald Trump a second term.
headline_main: 2020 Democrats Prepare to Debate in Shadow of Impeachment
headline_print_headline: 2020 Democrats Prepare to Debate in Shadow of Impeachment
